303
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:48,620
That's a good idea.

304
00:18:48,720 --> 00:18:49,159
No.

305
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,740
Wait.

306
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:54,740
So, what you two mean is...

307
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,319
What we mean is

308
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:58,519
that your initial script,

