Sometimes, sincerity is more important
than technique.

323
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:26,399
Okay.

324
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,980
I will definitely work hard.

325
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:29,980
Good.

326
00:19:30,040 --> 00:19:31,079
I've already talked

327
