510
00:25:34,360 --> 00:25:35,279
We have walked steadily

511
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:36,959
on this path

512
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:38,140
and solidly over the years.

513
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:40,660
This is related to the contributions
