1008
00:46:05,440 --> 00:46:06,079
Exactly.

1009
00:46:06,080 --> 00:46:06,759
Mr. Tang, now...

1010
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:08,519
Once public opinion is solidified,

1011
00:46:08,520 --> 00:46:10,439
